			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_64968523" name="comment_link_64968523" href="//yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23530227&amp;cid=64968523" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64968523)" >if you plan not to consent, stick with it</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64968523" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64968523); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
