	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64968695"><p><div class="quote"><p>Technically I think it's the money being accused of the crime.</p></div><p>Sadly, I though you were right and you are.<br>
Technically, civil asset forfeiture involves a government lawsuit against the personal property itself or, in legal terms, in rem. <br> <b>As strange as it may seem, the inanimate property, whether a yacht or a bag of cash, is the defendant in such a proceeding.</b></p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64968695">

